### Get all contacts (local)
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get single contact by id (local) - replace with a real id after seeding
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/PUT_A_VALID_ID_HERE

### Get all contacts (Render, once deployed) - replace with your Render URL
GET https://YOUR-APP-NAME.onrender.com/contacts

### Get single contact by id (Render)
GET https://YOUR-APP-NAME.onrender.com/contacts/PUT_A_VALID_ID_HERE
